des:
The Green Feathers skill is designed to be used with our wildlife and bird box cameras. This will allow you to view your camera through your Alexa Echo Show screen.

Once set up all you have to do is say "Alexa, show my bird box camera" and it will show up on the screen.

1. Download the Green Feathers app in app market then register an account or log in directly if you already have an account;
2. Configure your devices in Green Feathers app and give them a nickname;
3. Enable the Green Feathers skill. You'll be navigated to the login page where you can follow the instructions on the page to complete the linking;
4. Tell your Echo Show "Alexa, discover my devices". Wait for Alexa to say “Search complete”;
5. Now all setup is finished – you can enjoy the voice control of your cameras!
